e\",\"1rMFg0JQMQ\":\"Audit logs\",\"1wokJ79qDV\":\"Download on the App Store\",\"1yI27UHVWQ\":\"Get the developer newsletter\",\"2WJFp1YqEN\":\"Start in your terminal\",\"2b6AZVea7M\":\"Anton Biryukov, Staff Software Engineer\",\"3I6tohOmT8\":\"Thank you! You're subscribed.\",\"4OTeOUc7PT\":\"Yes. Claude Code runs locally in your terminal and talks directly to model APIs without requiring a backend server or remote code index. It also asks for permission before making changes to your files or running commands.\",\"4lOuLo24hP\":\"Early access to advanced Claude features\",\"5MDGuMLnEB\":\"Enter your email\",\"5a1X5/f0GE\":\"Team \u0026 Enterprise\",\"7GnV3M0ilx\":\"Code onboarding\",\"7NrmWSpPNp\":\"Everything in {previousPlan}, plus:\",\"7zyAzJqQJJ\":\"Sorry, there was a problem with your submission. Please try again later.\",\"9XGMrOTnKT\":\"How much does it cost to use?\",\"9l3FHo1rqB\":\"Claude Code is included with Team plan standard and premium seats. Includes self-serve seat management and usage credits at standard API rates.\",\"A61C8w9a82\":\"What should I use Claude for?\",\"AFiVmp/jhu\":\"Kick off coding tasks in Slack\",\"Auznb9aRrh\":\"Fergal Reid, VP of AI\",\"B1kbGgSfbf\":\"Download for Windows\",\"BB6lTqQOLY\":\"Explore plans\",\"BDUp/0Lp01\":\"Create files and execute code\",\"Bil1ISGOy5\":\"Your terminal is where real work happens. Claude Code connects with the tools that power development—deployment, databases, monitoring, version control. Rather than adding another interface to juggle, it enhances your existing stack.\",\"BwZb5mni5x\":\"Get Claude Code\",\"CDLJ0Wjq0x\":\"Enterprise\",\"CNfG9Dq1Zt\":\"From $100\",\"CQJzKN8cVI\":\"Claude Code works on macOS, Linux, and Windows. See full system requirements.\",\"D/ZD6IAZgu\":\"Seat price + usage\",\"D7vmeSqorj\":\"Memory across conversations\",\"DbJPLzWI00\":\"For everyday productivity\",\"FEmwkli1hU\":\"Generate code and visualize data\",\"FF8JcX97n6\":\"$$17\",\"FJ6r9Eufij\":\"Continue with Google\",\"FOwbsXm6VV\":\"Pay as you go with standard Claude API pricing. Deploy to unlimited developers with no per-seat fee or platform charges.\",\"Fg6Vy9QMJG\":\"$$0\",\"GMGlL/Lcsj\":\"\u003cb\u003eDynamic workflows:\u003c/b\u003e Tackle the most challenging tasks by executing across 10s to 100s of parallel subagents, and checking its work before anything reaches you.\",\"GP4bLAJKf8\":\"Predictable usage per seat\",\"GWoVQxhRVj\":\"Common workflows\",\"GagvZM9roV\":\"Higher output limits for all tasks\",\"GfJ5cvf3CF\":\"Even more Claude Code included in your Max plan. Great value for power users with the most access to Claude models.\",\"HF143K5NAr\":\"Claude is an artificial intelligence, trained by Anthropic using Constitutional AI to be safe, accurate, and secure — the trusted assistant for you to do your best work.\",\"HMbjivrCNV\":\"Is Claude Code secure?\",\"HU+0CefWLk\":\"Super powerful terminal integration. Works with all your CLI tools alongside any IDE.\",\"Hfxoyy1aNF\":\"Choose 5x or 20x more usage than Pro*\",\"Hnr5smjIWv\":\"Pay-as-you-go pricing with pooled usage across your org\",\"IgB6GUj3uH\":\"Individual\",\"Iv62ZyIGmq\":\"Claude Code's underst"])</script><script nonce="0aNxbr+Ww/r4jKqqXL73lQ==">self.__next_f.push([1,"anding of your codebase and dependencies enables it to make powerful, multi-file edits that work.\",\"JD3LFRaiXU\":\"Write, edit, and create content\",\"JLNwuE4tOW\":\"*\u003ca\u003eUsage limits apply.\u003c/a\u003e Prices and plans are subject to change at Anthropic's discretion.\",\"JWmizX/FBI\":\"What is fast mode on Claude Code?\",\"KorkNqY43b\":\"Fix software bugs faster with Claude\",\"KvrB2MkS1H\":\"Meet Claude\",\"LNXJWdoIN6\":\"Create what's exciting. Maintain what's essential.\",\"LRVkLV7Hgr\":\"Chat on web, iOS, Android, and on your desktop\",\"Lk6Bj3rToS\":\"\u003cstandard\u003e$20\u003c/standard\u003e/seat. Usage cost scales with model and task.\",\"LteDgy93R9\":\"What are the system requirements to run Claude Code?\",\"MRWcodfpX1\":\"5–20x more usage than Pro\",\"NPPnZiceNd\":\"Unlock more from Claude with desktop extensions\",\"Ne+gtmuqX2\":\"Early access to collaboration features\",\"NnoyhwhldS\":\"\u003cb\u003eComputer use:\u003c/b\u003e Claude now opens your apps, navigates your browser, and runs your dev tools to complete tasks.\",\"NvUZgo9/ND\":\"Set user and org spend limits\",\"NzrAGFVz6b\":\"Unlimited projects\",\"O+QGhrX2LT\":\"or\",\"O0tRsUvDJG\":\"With Claude, we're not just automating customer service—we're elevating it to truly human quality. This lets support teams think more strategically about customer experience and what makes interactions genuinely valuable.\",\"OUVgrjU/dw\":\"Fast mode is a high-speed configuration for Opus 4.8, making the model 2.5x faster at a higher cost per token. Fast mode is available:\",\"OatF5mAvNM\":\"What kinds of tasks can Claude Code handle?\",\"Oenbazr9Jm\":\"Draft and iterate on websites, graphics, documents, and code alongside your chat with Artifacts.\",\"Oz3oVE8beB\":\"Recommended for Claude Code \u0026 Cowork\",\"P6GgnebqRh\":\"Priority access at high traffic times\",\"QApUINIDYB\":\"Meets you where you code\",\"QFs5pskj1Z\":\"In research preview on Claude Code, and is priced at $30/$150 per million tokens.\",\"QrG/q/0nwX\":\"You can access Claude Code with a Claude Pro or Max plan, a Team or Enterprise plan premium seat, or a Claude Console account. \u003ca\u003eDownload Claude Code\u003c/a\u003e and sign in with your respective Claude or Console credentials.\",\"R/eOkjWqNU\":\"Pro\",\"RMOn5LTG7Q\":\"Claude Code runs in your terminal and works alongside your preferred IDE and development tools without requiring you to change your workflow. Claude Code can also use command line tools (like Git) and MCP servers (like GitHub) to extend its own capabilities using your tools.\",\"ROBSvgY5lo\":\"When used with a Claude Console account, Claude Code consumes API tokens at \u003ca\u003estandard API pricing\u003c/a\u003e.\",\"RRp63dkeIU\":\"What is Claude and how does it work?\",\"SZaT2AdIUl\":\"What developers are saying\",\"TFqOUdkTad\":\"Claude Code documentation\",\"TGDx1ikPDJ\":\"More usage*\",\"TJEhp8h+U3\":\"More Claude models\",\"TkDcZajDzk\":\"Latest feature announcements\",\"Txltt+43Pa\":\"Claude has five pricing plans available — Free, Pro, Max, Team, and Enterprise. The Free plan offers limited use with no payment required. \u003ca\u003eLearn more about available pricing plans\u003c/a\u003e.\",\"TyE4PlkMfX\":\"Via usage credits for users on subscription plans.\",\"TyVItC3Apb\":\"Integrate any context or tool through connectors with remote MCP\",\"TzE6GnXLOB\":\"How much does Claude Code cost?\",\"V3DZSAgwS0\":\"No commitment · Cancel anytime\",\"Vg6ctp2T0e\":\"200K context window\",\"Vn/B4Q2FzQ\":\"By continuing, you acknowledge Anthropic's \u003ca\u003ePrivacy Policy\u003c/a\u003e and agree to get occasional promotional emails and notifications.\",\"VvjKJpgcvg\":\"Access to Research\",\"W8nHSdskn0\":\"FAQ\",\"WGjpyApkxf\":\"Role-based access with fine grained permissioning\",\"XoZI2iCtxL\":\"Claude Design\",\"YKGWJSxqMY\":\"Read story\",\"YLao9+QH8h\":\"Please provide your email address if you'd like to receive our monthly developer newsletter. You can unsubscribe at any time.\",\"YYot3EpUou\":\"$$20\",\"Yg+jLKfIKn\":\"SCIM provisioning\",\"YuZ2EYYkhH\":\"How do I get started with Claude?\",\"ZRan5/6oUK\":\"Connect Slack and Google Workspace services\",\"Zz6QTaW0y5\":\"Available for macOS, Linux, and Windows.\",\"a3Xp8nfgoH\":\"Per seat / month. For teams of 5 to 150.\",\"aF7o2f3nQS\":\"Turn issues into PRs\",\"aT/oh4Nxvz\":\"Per standard seat per month (annual). Premium seats from \u003cpremium\u003e$100\u003c/pre"])</script><script nonce="0aNxbr+Ww/r4jKqqXL73lQ==">self.__next_f.push([1,"mium\u003e/mo.\",\"azQRa7pYOp\":\"View changelog\",\"bELf2s68U0\":\"Download for Linux\",\"bL/ieQDt4B\":\"How Anthropic teams use Claude Code\",\"cD9MYY3JiA\":\"\u003cb\u003eAgent view:\u003c/b\u003e One place to manage all your Claude Code sessions.\",\"cHXyPLuQFl\":\"Introduction to agentic coding\",\"cXJ/DmUVmm\":\"Claude in Excel\",\"ca6VLXmR5d\":\"Stop bouncing between tools. Claude Code integrates with GitHub, GitLab, and your command line tools to handle the entire workflow—reading issues, writing code, running tests, and submitting PRs—all from your terminal.\",\"dl29r7OlXE\":\"Ability to search the web\",\"epieNNdeXY\":\"Claude Code is moving our team up a level: we decide what needs to happen, and smooth the process so it can build and verify end-to-end. A big part of my job now is to keep as many instances of Claude Code busy as possible.\",\"fGpRdLrMdV\":\"Does Claude Code work with the Claude desktop app?\",\"fJ79V5uNwz\":\"Yes. Max, Pro, Team, and Enterprise users can access Claude Code on the Claude desktop app.\",\"fpD9g5c0+g\":\"Work with Claude directly in your codebase. Build, debug, and ship from your terminal, IDE, Slack, web, and more.\",\"fubYuebYh9\":\"Access anywhere\",\"gVc7XkWaqo\":\"Quick access from browser, mobile app, or Claude on desktop. Great for parallel work or on-the-go coding.\",\"gczcC5Leue\":\"Subscribe\",\"gym0t97hr3\":\"Yes. Max, Pro, Team, and Enterprise users can access Claude Code on the \u003ca\u003eClaude desktop app\u003c/a\u003e.\",\"h1KcNqCY5k\":\"*\u003ca\u003eUsage limits apply.\u003c/a\u003e Prices shown don't include applicable tax. Prices and plans are subject to change at Anthropic's discretion.\",\"h1ZCL0rm+U\":\"Using CLAUDE.md files\",\"h9g1IEUMWL\":\"Make powerful edits\",\"hJZwTSF8Wx\":\"Email address\",\"hcoACxj9cD\":\"Enterprise plan includes everything in the Team plan, plus advanced security, data, and user management. \u003ca\u003eLearn more here\u003c/a\u003e.\",\"hpjBFT7MBG\":\"Claude Code is included in your Max plan. Great value for everyday use in larger codebases.\",\"hvATMfbD6N\":\"Get started with Claude Code\",\"hy0YlmzQtV\":\"Share your best chats with your team to spark better ideas and move work forward on the Claude Team and Enterprise plans.\",\"iQYFHFpp2/\":\"Start building\",\"iZmBMJrb0b\":\"Create Projects and add knowledge so that you can deliver expert-level results with the Claude Pro, Team and Enterprise plans.\",\"ii5+AISEyS\":\"\u003ca\u003eUsage limits apply\u003c/a\u003e. Price and plans are subject to change at Anthropic's discretion.\",\"ilGFW+DK9E\":\"What could you do with Claude Code?\",\"jcwE2sEK9f\":\"Connects with your favorite command line tools\",\"jw+K5d+CdN\":\"When used with a Claude Console account, Claude Code consumes API tokens at standard API pricing.\",\"k4+9FsLhU8\":\"On consumption-based plans.\",\"kT9aRtqKCe\":\"Fast mode is a high-speed configuration for Opus 4.8, making the model 2.5x faster at a higher cost per token. Fast mode is available: In research preview on Claude Code, and is priced at $30/$150 per million tokens. On consumption-based plans. Via usage credits for users on subscription plans.\",\"kfTd44gfS5\":\"500K context window\",\"kkjl2vQekD\":\"Max\",\"l6yCDglZqT\":\"Continue with email\",\"lcjzsP/DJa\":\"Per month with annual subscription discount (\u003cannual\u003e$200\u003c/annual\u003e billed up front). \u003cmonthly\u003e$20\u003c/monthly\u003e if billed monthly.\",\"m0TzBiIhvZ\":\"Central billing and administration\",\"m7v1ahj/te\":\"Native extensions for VS Code (+ Cursor, Devin Desktop) and JetBrains IDEs.\",\"mENE7vJhVQ\":\"Extended thinking for complex work\",\"mofX8KnW9/\":\"Claude Code works on macOS, Linux, and Windows. \u003ca\u003eSee full system requirements\u003c/a\u003e.\",\"oJiyzDUmhQ\":\"Claude Code has dramatically accelerated our team's coding efficiency. I can now write EDA code in a notebook—pulling data, training a model, and evaluating it with basic metrics—and then ask Claude to convert that into a Metaflow pipeline. This process saves 1-2 days of routine (and often boring!) work per model.\",\"omjuNlvXVf\":\"Think fast,{br}build faster\",\"pCyFJadqy/\":\"Simon Last, Co-founder\",\"pIMYBlpmaw\":\"Analyze text and images\",\"pZ4CtGSlwT\":\"Try Claude\",\"pwc0DlEZo3\":\"You can access Claude Code with a Claude Pro or Max plan, a Team or Enterprise plan premium seat, or a Claude Console account. Download "])</script><script nonce="0aNxbr+Ww/r4jKqqXL73lQ==">self.__next_f.push([1,"Claude Code and sign in with your respective Claude or Console credentials.\",\"qSEmqaxK/a\":\"Download desktop app\",\"qank7+0V6w\":\"Continue with SSO\",\"qhHpS4CiBR\":\"Get Enterprise plan\",\"rsNxxABBT7\":\"Read documentation\",\"s8DKo7UP+l\":\"Share and collaborate with your team\",\"seQIayZV8Q\":\"Claude is a next generation AI assistant built by Anthropic and trained to be safe, accurate, and secure to help you do your best work.\",\"st9QnC8LFC\":\"Create with Claude\",\"tarJilR3bR\":\"How does Claude Code work with my existing tools?\",\"tf1lIh/bri\":\"Free\",\"trmBDXWSf3\":\"Brainstorm in chat, build in Cowork\",\"u8g3BII/vI\":\"Use Claude Code where you work\",\"uYv0mtuNZV\":\"Usage credits available at API rates\",\"uxizPhnuqF\":\"\u003ca\u003eUsage limits apply\u003c/a\u003e. Prices shown don't include applicable tax. Price and plans are subject to change at Anthropic's discretion.\",\"vKMj39KhGw\":\"Claude Code\",\"vMZxqST6IA\":\"Integrate with your editor\",\"vcxsGEi5U7\":\"If you can dream it, Claude can help you do it. Claude can process large amounts of information, brainstorm ideas, generate text and code, help you understand subjects, coach you through difficult situations, simplify your busywork so you can focus on what matters most, and so much more.\",\"wsUmh9XWBm\":\"Team\",\"xPocsFdsxB\":\"Download for macOS\",\"xi2NxiZh10\":\"Cowork\",\"ySTYWchNUB\":\"Free for everyone\",\"z/KFW3VRE0\":\"You can use Claude for your own personal use or create a Team account to collaborate with your teammates. \u003ca\u003eLearn more about Claude\u003c/a\u003e.\",\"z0VqPMdA5f\":\"Get Team plan\",\"zNhCk5LdVy\":\"Team and Enterprise\",\"zXcqZNmXkf\":\"Claude Code maps and explains entire codebases in a few seconds. It uses agentic search to understand project structure and dependencies without you having to manually select context files.\",\"zoXM3bL+ha\":\"Bring your knowledge\"},\"children\":\"$L10\"}]}]\n10:[\"$\",\"$L11\",null,{\"parallelRouterKey\":\"children\",\"error\":\"$undefined\",\"errorStyles\":\"$undefined\",\"errorScripts\":\"$undefined\",\"template\":[\"$\",\"$L12\",null,{}],\"templateStyles\":\"$undefined\",\"templateScripts\":\"$undefined\",\"notFound\":\"$undefined\",\"forbidden\":\"$undefined\",\"unauthorized\":\"$undefined\"}]\n13:[\"$\",\"style\",null,{\"nonce\":\"0aNxbr+Ww/r4jKqqXL73lQ==\",\"children\":\".transition-overlay { display: none !important; }\"}]\n1a:T1738,M200.168 110.625C190.376 110.625 181.647 108.688 173.98 104.813C166.355 100.896 160.397 95.4167 156.105 88.375C151.814 81.3333 149.668 73.25 149.668 64.125C149.668 54.4167 151.855 45.7917 156.23 38.25C160.647 30.7083 166.751 24.8542 174.543 20.6875C182.335 16.4792 191.189 14.375 201.105 14.375C207.064 14.375 213.001 15.0208 218.918 16.3125C224.876 17.5625 230.105 19.5208 234.605 22.1875V42.75H228.98C227.397 35.2083 224.293 29.7292 219.668 26.3125C215.085 22.8958 208.814 21.1875 200.855 21.1875C193.23 21.1875 186.897 22.8958 181.855 26.3125C176.814 29.7292 173.085 34.5 170.668 40.625C168.251 46.7083 167.043 53.7917 167.043 61.875C167.043 69.8333 168.397 76.9792 171.105 83.3125C173.814 89.6458 177.835 94.6458 183.168 98.3125C188.501 101.979 194.918 103.813 202.418 103.813C207.501 103.813 211.855 102.813 215.48 100.813C219.147 98.8125 222.23 96.0833 224.73 92.625C227.23 89.125 229.564 84.8333 231.73 79.75H237.605L233.605 102.313C229.272 105.104 224.105 107.188 218.105 108.563C212.105 109.938 206.126 110.625 200.168 110.625ZM243.168 103.938C245.626 103.646 247.543 103.271 248.918 102.813C250.335 102.313 251.355 101.646 251.98 100.813C252.605 99.9792 252.918 98.9167 252.918 97.625V29.5625L243.168 25.875V21.6875L262.793 14.375H267.793V97.6